METHOD

     [tomgdow]># This string 'has single' "and double" quotes and a $
     [tomgdow]> !:q

     [tomgdow]>'# This string '\''has single'\'' "and double" quotes and a $'
     [tomgdow]># This string 'has single' "and double" quotes and a $: command not found



REFERENCE
    Escaping strings in Bash using !:q
    https://til.simonwillison.net/til/til/bash_escaping-a-string.md
